\begin_layout Standard
Many different Lyapunov functions may exist for a system (i.e., they are not
 unique) and some may reveal more about a system than others.
 For example, Equation 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:example-locally-positive-definite-lyapunov-function"
