\begin_inset Formula $c$
\end_inset

 are linear continuous functions verifying the sign conditions
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\dot{x}\,b\left(\dot{x}\right)>0 & \qquad\text{for \;\ensuremath{\dot{x}}\ensuremath{\neq0}}\\
x\,c\left(x\right)>0 & \qquad\text{for \;\ensuremath{x}\ensuremath{\neq0}.}
\end{align*}

